<h1>Bramley Golf Club</h1>
<p class="subtitle"><strong>Continuous Improvement Programme — Committee &amp; Director Guide</strong></p>
<p class="version">Version 1.0 &nbsp;&bull;&nbsp; June 2026</p>

<hr>

<div class="toc">
<p class="toc-title">Contents</p>
<p>1. Programme overview</p>
<p>2. Roles and access levels</p>
<p>3. Signing in</p>
<p>4. The triage report</p>
<p>5. Understanding scores and bands</p>
<p>6. Views — Card view and Spreadsheet view</p>
<p>7. Filters and search</p>
<p>8. Managing submissions</p>
<p>9. Target dates</p>
